N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1261.3 - Aircraft subject to detainment for nonpayment of charges

State Regulations

The manager shall have authority to detain any aircraft
for nonpayment of storage charges due to the Port Authority for storage at an
air terminal. Notes
